[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "本劇情涉及活動劇情「失落的信仰～後篇～」與「愛如繁星傾注」的核心內容。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "下一個任務是找到「煉獄之鑰」與回收「煉獄文書」嗎。又是一件重大任務呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯。「煉獄之鑰」就如其名，是得到「煉獄文書」的關鍵之物。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "換言之，可能又將有新的「煉獄文書」被解放流入世間……是這麼一回事吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "這次任務可以說關係到伊利亞教會的命運是吧。所以，「煉獄之鑰」現在在哪？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "詳細情報還在精確調查中。正式任務會在鎖定目標地點後下達。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120195_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "只是，以現階段的情報而言，可以確定目標位在北方的雪國一帶。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120195_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "……唔，我對寒冷地帶不太在行耶。本大爺是負責腦力工作的，實在不想去過於嚴苛的工作環境啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "這次的任務，我認為就是看中你出色的腦力才會指派給你的喔？偶爾拿出點幹勁如何？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "正是。本次任務由於目標的性質具高機密性與高不確定性，所以，判斷兩位最適任。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120195_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "也就是說，涅因在使徒之中最值得信賴，且能依現場判斷臨機應變這點也備受期待。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……真是的，你這麼熱心解釋，聽得我都害臊了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0028.wav"], "content": "了解啦。既然如此備受期待，就不能辜負對吧。這次我會拿出真本事來的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "我很期待喔，涅因。讓我看看你的成長吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "所以說，能不能別再把我當小孩看了啊，雷米爾……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "數天後", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0068.wav"], "content": "呵，這東西真不錯。防寒效果非常好，穿起來也相當舒服。果然有特別訂製的價值。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但同樣地也花了不少錢……就當作是提前送給自己的星龍祭禮物吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120019_story/VO_CHR_120019_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "好，來把星龍樹立起來吧！麻煩來幫忙一下！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120019_01.png", "speakerName": "街上的人們1", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120014_story/VO_CHR_120014_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "好，我來了！交給我吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120014_01.png", "speakerName": "街上的人們2", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "呵呵，必須好好裝飾它才行呢！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "街上的人們3", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "……整個城鎮完全已經是星龍祭的氣氛了呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不過，雖然很難過，這都是和本大爺無關的事。使徒的工作就是全年無休這點很辛苦啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120038_story/VO_CHR_120038_STORY_0076.wav"], "content": "找、找到你了！爸爸……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "嗯？爸爸？喂喂，我看起來有那麼老嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120038_story/VO_CHR_120038_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "啊……對不起。因為你穿的衣服和爸爸平常穿的大衣顏色一樣……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗚……爸爸……到底跑到哪裡去了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "（是迷路的小孩嗎……看來是和父親走散了呢。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120038_story/VO_CHR_120038_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "嗚……嗚嗚……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喂、喂，別哭啦。這樣不是搞得很像是我把你弄哭的嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120038_story/VO_CHR_120038_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "嗚……嗚嗚……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "真是的，拿你沒辦法耶……我來幫你找吧。你父親有什麼特徵？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（這是來自東方國家的服裝。他們恐怕是旅行者……那麼至少，要推測他父親的移動路徑會很容易。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊！找到了！是爸爸！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120198_story/VO_CHR_120198_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "……！啊，太好了！終於找到你了……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120095_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "呼，這樣就圓滿結束了。由如此有能的本大爺來處理，事情就是這麼簡單啦。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "難道說，是你陪我兒子一起找的嗎？真是太感謝了。多虧有你，我們才能會合。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120095_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗚……爸爸……！爸爸……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120198_story/VO_CHR_120198_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "嗯……對不起。都怪我看異國風景看得太入迷，才沒注意到和你走散了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120095_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是我不好，請你原諒我……對了，我買個禮物送你當作賠罪吧。要買什麼都可以喔？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120095_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120038_story/VO_CHR_120038_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "咦？真的嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120198_story/VO_CHR_120198_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "嗯。這個國家有個叫做星龍祭的節慶，聽說大家會在這時送禮物給重要的人。就當作是星龍祭禮物送你吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120095_01.png", "speakerName": "父親", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120038_story/VO_CHR_120038_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "哇～太好了！那我要買剛才在店裡看到的那個！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "男孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "哎呀哎呀，小孩子真是單純啊。上一秒還以為他會繼續大哭大鬧，結果一個禮物就讓他笑成那樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……禮物、嗎。這麼說來，我以前也……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "咦？這個，我真的可以收下嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "年幼的涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗯，當然可以。今天是星龍祭，所以不必客氣，收下它吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "謝謝你，雷米爾！我會很珍惜它的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "年幼的涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（和雷米爾一起慶祝星龍祭，坦率地為收到禮物感到開心……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "（我也曾經那麼天真無邪啊……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……不過，回憶難為情的往事就到此為止。現在的我可是有任務在身。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為了隨時都能應對聖德芬的召集，必須先做好各種準備呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "那麼，其他需要的東西是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0086.wav"], "content": "啊！前輩，你終於回來了……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "嗯？怎麼了，琵儂。看妳面有難色，發生什麼事了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0081.wav"], "content": "對！其實呢──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110365031, "title": "純真的記憶"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "（真是的。還想說琵儂碰到了什麼麻煩……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "啊，這個緞帶，真好看耶……啊啊但是，那個髮夾也很……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "（沒想到只是無法決定星龍祭要送什麼禮物給加百列……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "那個！前輩你覺得哪一個比較適合加百列呢！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "……別問我。這種事妳自己想。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "又開始嫌麻煩了……請你好好回答啦，前輩。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "雖然我確實是覺得麻煩，但並不只是那樣。就算現在我回答了，也幫不上妳的忙。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "但是……我自己沒辦法下決定，所以才想聽聽前輩的意見……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "那麼，假設我現在說出自己的意見，並決定用那個當禮物好了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但這樣一來，真的能算是琵儂為加百列選的禮物嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！這、這個……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "要送的禮物，正因為是琵儂為了加百列精心挑選的，才有價值不是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0013.wav"], "content": "……是。正如前輩所說。這禮物的目的是為了向重要的人表達感謝的心意……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "真是給你添麻煩了。我會好好自己選擇的……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，那樣加百列也會比較開心的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "還讓你特地陪我來，不好意思……啊，既然難得來了，前輩要不要也買個禮物回去？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……不，我就不必了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "這樣嗎……？前輩不向雷米爾表示感謝的心意嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯。那種事不適合我。有認真的琵儂後輩做就夠了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "想像一下如果我反常地做這種事會變怎樣？眼前馬上就能浮現那個性格惡劣的天使嘲笑我的景象對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "唔……這、這麼一說確實是……但是……真的沒關係嗎？前輩不會覺得後悔嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "後悔……？為什麼會後悔？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "後悔沒有向養育自己的重要對象表達感謝的心意。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我們的任務總是與死亡為鄰……而天使們也確實在那時候失去過一次性命……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喝啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "天使們", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我不能比那孩子還早逝去啊……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "騙人的吧……喂……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "那時候，我非常後悔。想著自己都還沒向養育我長大的加百列表達足夠的謝意……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以，我決定這次的星龍祭要和加百列一起慶祝，並且將感謝的心意好好告訴她。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "想說的話，一定要在能說的時候就說出來……不然感覺又會後悔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "難道前輩沒有嗎？沒有不對重要對象說，就會後悔的話語……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "……也不是沒有。但是很遺憾，那並不是表達感謝的話。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而是想和雷米爾並肩同行，充滿決心與覺悟的話。而那些話，在他復活的時候已經說過了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "這種話說過一遍就夠了。畢竟一直掛在嘴邊，只會淪為陳腐的言論。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0079.wav"], "content": "確實……感謝的心意不論說幾次都可以，但決心與覺悟的話……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "對吧？所以我就不必了。真的想說的話，我已經說過了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "我知道了。不好意思多管閒事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "嗯，明白就好。那麼，妳不用在意我，好好去挑選禮物吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "好的！……嗯～緞帶跟髮夾，到底哪一個比較好呢……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "謝謝你，前輩！這樣一來，我就能好好將感謝的心意傳達給加百列了！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "那很好啊。加百列想必會喜極而泣吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "先說，我不是在開玩笑喔？妳不覺得那傢伙會因為太感動，而發自內心大哭出來嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那、那個……！唔唔，因為實在太好想像了，總覺得開始有點不好意思……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "哈哈哈，儘管害臊吧。如果要打消送禮物的念頭，現在還來得及喔？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110366_story/VO_CHR_110366_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "才、才不要呢！我已經決定了！再也不想後悔……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110366_02.png", "speakerName": "琵儂", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "是嗎。那麼，要好好把那禮物交給她喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（……不過，後悔……嗎？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（雷米爾消失的時候，我內心抱持的想法，已經都告訴他了。但如果同樣的事情再發生一次……？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（如果就這樣沒對雷米爾表示感謝，那傢伙就消失的話……那我……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110365032, "title": "珍貴的訊息"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "唔呃……！嘖，這下有點棘手了啊……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "那敵人的力量，甚至超越了撒旦。這樣下去的話……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "沒辦法了。既然如此，只能採取最後手段……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雷米爾……？你打算做什麼？該不會……要像那時候一樣，賭上自己的性命……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0054.wav"], "content": "喂，快住手……雷米爾！拜託！快點回來！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我還沒有傳達給你！向你傳達感謝的心意……！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雷米爾────！！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……啊！雷米爾呢……？還有，那個敵人呢……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……是夢、嗎。真是的，我居然會夢到這種糟糕的夢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "因為這樣，我好像還在情急之下講了些奇怪的話……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "還沒有向雷米爾傳達感謝的心意，之類的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "…………想說的話一定要在能說的時候說出來，不然就會後悔……嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "琵儂說的話或許有點道理呢。我也像她一樣準備禮物……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "呃，不對不對，那種事一點都不符合我的個性吧。這才不是本大爺會做的事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "涅因，可以占用你一點時間嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "喔哇！？雷、雷米爾！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "喔？怎麼了？為何那麼驚慌。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不、沒有，沒什麼事……比起這個，你有什麼事？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "北方城鎮的特別任務，我有點擔心你是否已經準備妥當。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "畢竟你很散漫，就像是那種找理由不做功課，直到最後一刻才慌忙交出來的小孩一樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0029.wav"], "content": "你在講多久以前的事啊，雷米爾……我已經不是小鬼了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "全都準備好啦。作為一個成熟的大人，我會把該做的事情好好做完的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那我就安心了。這表示你也有所成長呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "……但是，你房間的慘狀還是跟小時候一模一樣。既然你說已經是大人了，偶爾也打掃一下房間如何？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "別多管閒事啦！這個性格惡劣的天使！沒別的事就快點出去！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "可惡的雷米爾……挑人毛病就跟呼吸一樣自然。雖然說我的房間確實是有那麼一點髒亂……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……這麼說來我準備好的東西在哪？應該是在這附近……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "聖水在……喔，有了有了。聖光之環也……好好在這裡。再來就是隨身攜帶的緊急糧食……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "……嗯？怎麼會找不到？我應該都買齊了才對啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "嘖……找不到。沒辦法，再出門去買一次吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……這樣就行了。真是的，下次可不能再搞丟。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "歡迎光臨～！現在起將開始限時特賣～！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "店員", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "這架上的商品全部都打七折！歡迎盡情選購～！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "店員", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "喔，還真幸運呢。既然機會難得，就稍微看看吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喔，這耳環真好看啊。感覺很適合雷米爾。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "……我如果送這個他或許會很高興吧……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……不對，我怎麼又……！就說這不符合我的個性了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "這位客人，您的眼光真好！這個商品就只有這一副而已唷！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "店員", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "咦？真的嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是的～！這是職人精心製作出的最高級自信之作喔！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "店員", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "真的非常好看對不對～！怎麼樣，要試戴看看嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "店員", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "啊，不……戴的人不是我……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120018_story/VO_CHR_120018_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "原來如此，要當禮物對吧！我們有提供包裝的服務喔！啊，要不要寫張小卡片呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "店員", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不，那個，我還沒有決定要買……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "謝謝惠顧～！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120018_01.png", "speakerName": "店員", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "一個不小心，就買下去了。該怎麼辦呢，這個……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……不過，既然都買了也沒辦法。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "就把它當禮物送給雷米爾吧。畢竟這耳環也很適合他。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_01.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110365033, "title": "感謝的禮物"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "……那麼，接下來的問題就是要在何時用什麼方式把禮物交給雷米爾了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "（其他使徒和天使在的時候也不能送啊……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（尤其絕對不能在琵儂面前。我都已經講了一堆送禮物不合個性那種耍帥的話……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（果然只能趁雷米爾單獨行動的時候送了吧……！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（好……就是現在！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "雷米爾，你現在有空嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，怎麼了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0013.wav"], "content": "啊～就是……其實、啊……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（啊，可惡！為什麼說不出口啊！？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（輕描淡寫又巧妙地說一句「這是代表長久以來的感謝」，然後把東西交出去就好了吧！？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "怎麼了嗎，涅因？你好像不太方便說的樣子……要不然我們換個地方？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，在這裡就可以了。並不是什麼大不了的事情。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（沒錯……！不要在意太多！快速地把東西交出去！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "（對方可是那個性格惡劣的天使喔！？拖越久越會被過度解讀，到最後一定會被恥笑一番！！）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雷米爾……！這、這個──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "稍等一下。聖德芬來聯繫了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "啊、嗯……我知道了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "（嘖……時機真差。本來感覺能交給他了的說……可惡的聖德芬。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "嗯？等等，聖德芬？也就是說，該不會是上次那個……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "沒錯。是之前和你提過的特別任務。她要緊急召集我們。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "專心聆聽。「煉獄之鑰」的所在處已經掌握了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120195_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "地點在北方雪國，被視為星龍祭發祥地的城鎮。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120195_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120195_story/VO_CHR_120195_STORY_0086.wav"], "content": "使徒涅因、天使雷米爾，請兩位立刻前往當地找到「煉獄之鑰」並回收「煉獄文書」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120195_01.png", "speakerName": "聖德芬", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "了解。涅因也已經準備好了對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯，已經都準備萬全了。但是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "怎麼了，有什麼問題嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "…………不，沒什麼。不必在意。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "任務了解──使徒涅因，奉神之威名予以制裁。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "……好。任務中會用到的東西都備齊了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只是……這包裝精美的禮物，在任務中是用不到的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "……那麼，出發吧。接下來就是工作的時間了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就這樣，涅因與雷米爾一同前往星龍祭發祥城鎮。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "他們在該地幾經波折，最終成功回收了新的「煉獄文書」。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……但是在完成任務並返回時，已經錯過了星龍祭當日。", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……唉，真是困難的任務。如果不是有能的本大爺，可能會有任務失敗的危險呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "再來……就剩下該如何處理這禮物。但是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "……這次就先放棄吧。錯過時機才送禮物，沒有什麼比這還遜的了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "雖然對製作的職人，還有把這包裝得非常漂亮的小姐很過意不去……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "聽說星龍祭時在女神的旨意下會發生奇蹟……但女神並沒有對我微笑嗎。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "果然女神大人，也覺得不該做不符合個性的事而苦笑著吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110365034, "title": "諷刺的任務"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "將雷米爾的禮物丟棄的幾天後──", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0085.wav"], "content": "涅因，你今天有安排行程嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "嗯？我是沒什麼特別的預定……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "那太好了。請跟我一起來。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？是要去哪裡……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "跟我來就知道了喔。那麼，走吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "喂、喂喂……！？這桌看起來很高級的料理是！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "來，吃吧。這些都是為你點的喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "為了我……？怎麼回事？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "等下再說。趁料理還沒涼掉前趕快開動吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "總覺得有哪裡不對勁……但就這樣把料理放涼也確實很失禮。那就先開動吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0067.wav"], "content": "呼……吃飽了。好吃到感覺要升天了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……所以呢？為什麼要突然為我準備這種豪華大餐？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "呵呵，其實呢……這一頓是答謝你送我禮物的回禮唷。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "禮物……！？你、你在說什麼？我可不記得有送你什麼……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "哦，是那樣嗎？……那麼，這又是什麼呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "什麼……！？那個小盒子是！？我應該把它丟到垃圾桶了才對啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "你的房間實在太過髒亂，所以我就想說幫你打掃一下。這是在那時候發現的喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "嘖……居然做那種多餘的事。我就在想房間怎麼變乾淨了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "如果不喜歡我多管閒事的話，好好把房間打掃乾淨不就行了？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……算了。先不說打掃的事，重點不在那裡。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0034.wav"], "content": "總之，你看到我丟掉的禮物……就只是這樣。我可沒說那個是要送你的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "那還真是奇怪耶？小卡片上是署名要給我的喔？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0064.wav"], "content": "唔……！？糟糕，我都忘記當時被店員的業務嘴給說動……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好了，這下你已經無法狡辯了吧。老實回答我。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "你為什麼，都特地準備禮物了卻不交給我呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不……那是因為……該怎麼說呢……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "如果你很難說出口的話，就讓我來猜看看吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0063.wav"], "content": "一直錯過送禮時機剛好又要出任務，然後星龍祭就過了……大概是這樣對吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0018.wav"], "content": "嘖……對啦，就是你說的那樣啦。反正那麼遜地送你禮物，也只會被嘲笑吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "涅因……你真的是個無可救藥的笨蛋呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "什麼……！？你說這話是什麼意思啦！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就是字面上的意思啊。真是的，你到底把我想成是什麼啊……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "我不會嘲笑你的。來自重要的你所送的禮物，我收到當然會很開心啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雷米爾……真的嗎……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "嗯，當然。我才不會在這種事情上撒謊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "啊，但是會稍微挖苦你一下吧。你都自詡是有能之人，就不能把事情做得更俐落一點嗎……這樣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0038.wav"], "content": "唔……！這個性格惡劣的天使！只不過是從嘲笑變成挑剔，結果還是要說些討人厭的話！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "那是當然的。畢竟我必須讓你繼續成長才行。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你不是想與我並肩同行嗎？既然這樣，任何事都必須做到與我同等程度才行。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "至少我在送禮的時候，不會狼狽地錯過時機喔？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "……嘖。確實是這樣。被你這麼說完全無法反駁。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "真是討厭啊。為什麼父親的背影，會這麼高大呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0019.wav"], "content": "呵呵，要不是這樣的話，就無法表現給孩子看了啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "……哼，隨你高興怎麼說吧。總而言之，明年星龍祭時我會瀟灑地將禮物送給你的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_210132_story/VO_DRG_210132_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……嗯，明年再努力吧。我很期待你有更進一步的成長喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/210132_01.png", "speakerName": "雷米爾", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（要答謝至今的養育之恩，至少要等到明年了呢。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（不管怎樣，我都還有許多事要從這傢伙身上學習……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110365_story/VO_CHR_110365_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "（在成長到能與雷米爾並肩同行時，一定要挺起胸膛、堂堂正正地謝謝他一直以來的照顧……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110365_03.png", "speakerName": "涅因", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110365035, "title": "鳶與鷹"}]